  <title>
    <phrase lang="en">Navigation Window</phrase>
    <phrase lang="cs">Navigační okno</phrase>
    <phrase lang="de">Navigationsfenster</phrase>
    <phrase lang="fr">Fenêtre de navigation</phrase>
    <phrase lang="it">Finestra di navigazione</phrase>
    <phrase lang="no">Navigeringsvindauget</phrase>
    <phrase lang="zh_CN">导航窗口</phrase>
  </title>


  <indexterm lang="en">
    <primary>Navigation window</primary>
    <secondary>View Navigation window</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="cs"><primary>Navigační okno</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="de"><primary>Navigationsfenster</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="de"><primary>Ansichtsnavigation</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="fr">
    <primary>Fenêtre de navigation</primary>
    <secondary>Afficher la fenêtre de navigation</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="it"><primary>Finestra di navigazione</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="no">
    <primary>Vismenyen</primary>
    <secondary>Navigeringsvindauget</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="no"><primary>Navigeringsvindauget</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="zh_CN"><primary>导航窗口</primary></indexterm>


  <para lang="en">
    The <guimenuitem>Navigation Window</guimenuitem> command opens the
    <link linkend="gimp-navigation-dialog">navigation window</link>. This
    allows you to easily navigate through the image, to set zoom levels and
    to move the visible parts of the image. You can find more information
    about using it in the <link
    linkend="gimp-navigation-dialog">Navigation dialog</link> chapter.
  </para>
  <para lang="cs">
    Tato nabídka otvírá navigační okno, které usnadňuje pohyb a orientaci
    v obrázku a změnu přiblížení. Způsob používání tohoto okna je popsán
    v části <link linkend="gimp-navigation-dialog">Navigační dialog</link>.
  </para>
  <para lang="de">
    Mit diesem Kommando können Sie den Dialog <link
    linkend="gimp-navigation-dialog">Ansichtsnavigation</link> aufrufen.
    Dieser ermöglicht es Ihnen, sehr komfortabel durch das Bild zu navigieren,
    Vergrößerungsstufen einzustellen und den sichtbaren Bildausschnitt zu
    verschieben.
  </para>
  <para lang="fr">
    Ce menu ouvre une fenêtre de navigation qui permet de zoomer et de se
    déplacer dans l'image. Son utilisation est décrite
    au chapitre <link linkend="gimp-navigation-dialog">Dialogue de
    navigation</link>.
  </para>
  <para lang="it">
    Il comando <guimenuitem>Finestra di navigazione</guimenuitem> apre
    l'omonima <link linkend="gimp-navigation-dialog">Finestra di
    navigazione</link>. Essa permette di spostarsi facilmente
    sull'immagine, di impostare livelli di zoom e di spostare le parti
    visibili dell'immagine. Si possono trovare informazioni aggiuntive sul
    suo uso nel capitolo <link linkend="gimp-navigation-dialog">Finestra di
    dialogo di navigazione</link>.
  </para>
  <para lang="no">
    Kommandoen <guimenuitem>Navigeringsvindauget</guimenuitem> opnar
    <!--PENDING:no <link
    linkend="gimp-navigation-dialog"--><quote>Navigasjonsvindauget</quote><!--/link-->
    som gjer deg i stand til å navigera gjennom biletet, setje zoom-nivå
    og å flytte den synlege delen av biletet. Du finn meir om dette i
    kapitlet <!--PENDING:no <link
    linkend="gimp-navigation-dialog"-->Navigeringsdialogen<!--/link-->.
  </para>
  <para lang="zh_CN">
    该菜单项打开导航窗口，其中可以缩放和移动图像。它的用法请看<link
    linkend="gimp-navigation-dialog">导航对话框</link>。
  </para>


  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Activating the Command</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Aktivace dialogu</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Aufruf des Kommandos</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Appel de la commande</phrase>
      <phrase lang="it">Attivazione del comando</phrase>
      <phrase lang="no">Aktivering</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">开启对话框</phrase>
    </title>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          You can access this command from the image menubar through
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>V</accel>iew</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Na<accel>v</accel>igation Window</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>,
        </para>

        <para lang="cs">
          Tento příkaz lze vyvolat volbou
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>Zobrazení</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Navigační okno</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice> z nabídky okna obrázku.
        </para>

        <para lang="de">
          Der Menüeintrag kann aus dem Bildfenster
          erreicht werden:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>An<accel>s</accel>icht</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Navi<accel>g</accel>ationsfenster</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>

        <para lang="fr">
          Cette commande se trouve dans
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>A</accel>ffichage</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Fenêtre de na<accel>v</accel>igation</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>

        <para lang="it">
          È possibile accedere a questo comando dalla barra del menu
          immagine tramite
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>V</accel>isualizza</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Finestra di na<accel>v</accel>igazione</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>,
        </para>

        <para lang="no">
          Du får tilgang til denne undermenyen på biletmenyen via
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>Vis</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Navigeringsvindauget</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>

        <para lang="zh_CN">
          该命令在<guimenuitem>图像&gt;查看/导航窗口</guimenuitem>。
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          or by using the keyboard shortcut
           <keycombo>
            <keycap>Shift</keycap>
            <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
            <keycap>N</keycap>
          </keycombo>.
        </para>

        <para lang="cs">
          Ve výchozím nastavení lze Navigační ono vyvolat
          i klávesovou zkratkou <keycap>Shift+Ctrl+N</keycap>.
        </para>

        <para lang="de">
          Alternativ können Sie das Tastenkürzel
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Umschalt</keycap><keycap>Strg</keycap><keycap>N</keycap>
          </keycombo>
          verwenden.
        </para>

        <para lang="fr">
          La combinaison de touches
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Shift</keycap>
            <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
            <keycap>N</keycap>
          </keycombo>
          activera la Fenêtre de navigation.
        </para>

        <para lang="it">
          o usando la scorciatoia da tastiera
           <keycombo>
            <keycap>Maiusc</keycap>
            <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
            <keycap>N</keycap>
          </keycombo>.
        </para>

        <para lang="no">
          eller med snarvegen
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>I</keycap>
          </keycombo>.
        </para>

        <para lang="zh_CN">
          <keycap>Shift+Ctrl+N</keycap>执行导航窗口。
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem lang="en;fr;it;no">
        <para lang="en">
          You can also access it more rapidly by clicking on the
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="../images/using/stock-navigation-16.png" />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
          icon in the lower right corner of the image window.
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
           Vous pouvez y accéder plus rapidement en cliquant sur l'icône
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="../images/using/stock-navigation-16.png" />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon> située dans le coin en bas à droite de la fenêtre
          d'image.
       </para>
        <para lang="it">
          È anche possibile accedervi più rapidamente facendo clic sull'icona
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="../images/using/stock-navigation-16.png" />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
          presente nell'angolo in basso a destra della finestra immagine.
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          Den enklaste metoden er likevel å klikke på ikonet
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="../images/using/stock-navigation-16.png" />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
          i nedre, høgre hjørne av biletvindauget.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
